20. CTA interface
-----------------
Energy dispersion has been added to the CTA module. The class
GCTAEdispPerfTable implements a simple Gaussian energy dispersion that
is based on the energy dispersion rms value provided in the ASCII
performance files.


21. COMPTEL interface
---------------------
None
